Note on the Main WPP Project
-----------------------------

While SQTP and its libraries are MIT licensed, the main WPP project that
implements the SQTP server is licensed under GPL 3.0. This means:

  * SQTP Protocol Specification: MIT (this file)
  * SQTP JavaScript Libraries: MIT (this file)
  * WPP Server Implementation: GPL 3.0 (see main LICENSE file)

This dual-licensing approach allows:
  1. Anyone to implement SQTP clients/servers under any license
  2. The reference JavaScript libraries to be used freely
  3. The WPP server implementation to remain GPL 3.0

For questions about licensing, please contact the WPP Project maintainers.
